{"tid":661449,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★恐怖升降機：同類意外香港罕見　國內曾多次奪命","createTime":"2018-05-11T14:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T16:27:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a199d7e8cbcdc08d4d9b19e9463d8c8eac60dd20","tid":661449,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"升降機未到但門自動打開釀意外，在香港較罕見，近年均沒有發生過，惟在國內卻不時發生，較嚴重一宗發生於17年2月3日，遼寧瀋陽「瑞家景峰」屋苑一部升降機運行期間，突然從28樓急墜至3樓，4名乘客被困；與此同時，28樓的升降機門卻無故打開，一對分別43及44歲的姓楊叔姪失足踏空，雙雙墮斃在升降機廂頂部。<br />\n<br />\n另在16年1月29日，一名26歲女子手抱5個月大女兒，在陝西西安陽光新地小區，擬從31樓搭升降機落樓，詎料升降機未到門已打開，兩母女同墮至5至6樓間的升降機頂部亡。<br />\n<br />\n15年11月11日，一名30餘歲男子在廣東珠海金灣區三灶鎮一酒店4樓等電梯，他背靠着升降機門，突然升降機門打開，但內裏沒有𨋢箱，他直墮槽底身亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180511/photo/bkn-20180511183955059-0511_00822_001_03b.jpg?20180511195751\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180511%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180511183955059-0511_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20180511195751&h=c6d7ed6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n16年1月，母女在陝西西安陽光新地小區墮𨋢槽亡。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180511/bkn-20180511183955059-0511_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402882b1634e54a901634e8482d30a02\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180511%2Fbkn-20180511183955059-0511_00822_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dhk_news%26eventid%3D402882b1634e54a901634e8482d30a02&d=79svys0VV8dejz5Takm7ENWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=9c641813\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180511/bkn-20180511183955059-0511_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402882b1634e54a901634e8482d30a02</a>"},{"pid":"fe9575f2cffd7b3aa53cf34ac086cd9f3e777191","tid":661449,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T14:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/btjb-fyrwsqi0767868.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2Fbtjb-fyrwsqi0767868.png&h=b09c5666&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a77a8d3f98109818e7f6019cf89603191f0fd1ac","tid":661449,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T14:39:08.000Z","msg":"香港罕見　國內曾多次<br />\n<br />\n國內&gt;香港<br />\n<br />\n或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"a091dc5e14b226209d547ef85a933b75f7996c0e","tid":661449,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a77a8d3f98109818e7f6019cf89603191f0fd1ac","tid":661449,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T14:39:08.000Z","msg":"香港罕見　國內曾多次<br />\n<br />\n國內&gt;香港<br />\n<br />\n或成最大贏家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"6e7da321f909a05ea0df7a5ad38a799e5076368d","tid":661449,"uid":48334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T14:43:35.000Z","msg":"中國又贏，對外輸出意外"},{"pid":"e36f55ea5228f8630fafb4a1361a1b7a1fb939eb","tid":661449,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:16:54.000Z","msg":"贏"},{"pid":"e799e99e2e092c3899253e0b3dd8db756a9fe4b4","tid":661449,"uid":59567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:27:46.000Z","msg":"一家人嘛，不要那麼計較，中國死幾件香港才一件半件，不是已經很好？"}]}